l Atake\u2019 Spends Second Week at No. 1 on Billboard 200 Albums Chart|last=Caufield|first=Keith|website=[[Billboard Hot 100|Billboard]]|date=March 22, 2020}}</ref>\n* RIAA Certification: uncertified \n|-\n| Sheck Wes - ''Hell 2 Paradise''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/sheckwes/status/1239624547529351169|title=We announced HELL 2 PARADISE in 2018 , a day after MUDBOY , it\u2019s the second album,  dgaf about what\u2019s happening or the outcome , it\u2019s just gonna outdrum your eardrum,|via=[[Twitter]]|date=March 17, 2020}}</ref>\n* Released: 2020\n* Label: Cactus Jack, Interscope, GOOD\n* Formats: N/A\n|\n* Chart position: uncharted\n* RIAA Certification: uncertified\n|}\n\n===Compilation albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Album details\n!Details\n|-\n| style=\"text-align; center\" | 2019\n| JackBoys (with Travis Scott) - ''[[JackBoys]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/jackboys/1492785997|title=JACKBOYS by JACKBOYS & Travis Scott on Apple Music|via=[[Apple Music]]|date=December 27, 2019}}</ref>\n* Released: December 27, 2019\n* Label: Cactus Jack, Epic\n* Formats: CD, LP, cassette, digital download, streaming\n|\n* Chart position: #1 U.S.<ref name=\"JackBoys Billboard\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8547503/travis-scott-jackboys-billboard-artist-100-number-one|title=Travis Scott-Led Jackboys Launch at No. 1 on Billboard Artist 100|last=Zellner|first=Xander|date=January 7, 2020}}</ref>\n* RIAA Certification: Gold\n|}\n\n===Other charted songs===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of songs, with selected chart positions, showing year released and album name\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em;\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"5\" | Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\" | Album \n|-\n! scope=\"col\" st